#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kooka; allows you to scan, save and view in any image format that &Qt; "
"supports, and can perform optical character recognition."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; vam omogoča skeniranje, shranjevanje in ogled v katerem koli formatu "
"slike, ki ga &Qt; podpira in lahko izvaja optično prepoznavanje znakov."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>OCR</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>OCR</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scanner"
msgstr "Skener"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kooka; is an application that provides access to scanner hardware using the "
"<ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">SANE</ulink> library. Therefore, "
"the <acronym>SANE</acronym> package must be installed to use &kooka;."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; je aplikacija, ki omogoča dostop do strojne opreme optičnega "
"bralnika z uporabo knjižnice <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/"
"\">SANE</ulink>. Zato mora biti za uporabo &kooka; nameščen paket "
"<acronym>SANE</acronym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kooka; allows you to scan, save and view in any image format that &Qt; "
"supports."
msgstr ""
"&kooka; vam omogoča skeniranje, shranjevanje in ogled v katerem koli formatu "
"slike, ki ga &Qt; podpira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Character recognition is also provided by using the open source <ulink url="
"\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net/\">GOCR</ulink> or <ulink url=\"http://www.gnu."
"org/software/ocrad/ocrad.html\">OCRAD</ulink> programs, or the commercial "
"<ulink url=\"https://rerecognition.com/en/products/kadmos-icr-ocr/\">KADMOS</"
"ulink> library. You have to install at least one of these software packages "
"to use this functionality. After character recognition is complete, a "
"spellcheck is automatically started for the recognized material. You can "
"edit the content in the <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> window and export it as "
"plain text."
msgstr ""
"Prepoznavanje znakov je na voljo tudi z uporabo odprtokodnega <ulink url="
"\"http://jocr.sourceforge.net/\">GOCR</ulink> ali <ulink url=\"http://www."
"gnu.org/software/ ocrad/ocrad.html\">OCRAD</ulink> ali komercialno knjižnico "
"<ulink url=\"https://rerecognition.com/en/products/kadmos-icr-ocr/\">KADMOS</"
"ulink>. Za uporabo te funkcije morate namestiti vsaj enega od teh "
"programskih paketov. Ko je prepoznavanje znakov končano, se samodejno zažene "
"preverjanje črkovanja za prepoznano gradivo. Vsebino lahko urejate v oknu "
"<guilabel>OCR</guilabel> in jo izvozite kot navadno besedilo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Application Instructions"
msgstr "Navodila za uporabo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The web site <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">http://www.sane-"
"project.org</ulink> has information about supported scanners. Refer to it "
"before purchasing a scanner, if possible."
msgstr ""
"Spletno mesto <ulink url=\"http://www.sane-project.org/\">http://www.sane-"
"project.org</ulink> vsebuje informacije o podprtih skenerjih. Če je mogoče, "
"ga preberite pred nakupom optičnega bralnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>The &kooka; Main Window</title>"
msgstr "<title>&kooka; Glavno okno</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kooka; Main Window</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kooka; Glavno okno</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &kooka; from a console by simply entering <userinput><command>kooka</"
"command></userinput> or select it from the <guilabel>Graphics</guilabel> "
"submenu in the application starter. Create a link on the desktop, which uses "
"a scanner icon, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Zaženi &kooka; iz konzole tako, da preprosto vnesete "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command></userinput> ali ga izberete v podmeniju "
"<guilabel>Grafika</guilabel> v zaganjalniku aplikacij. Ustvarite povezavo na "
"namizju, ki po želji uporablja ikono optičnega bralnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use &kooka; only for optical character recognition without connecting to "
"a scanner start the application in gallery mode with "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command> <option>-g</option></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo &kooka; samo za optično prepoznavanje znakov brez povezave s "
"skenerjem zaženite aplikacijo v galerijskem načinu z "
"<userinput><command>kooka</command> <option>-g</option></userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The main window in &kooka; consists of three frames. At the top, see both "
"icon and a menu panels. Use the mouse to enlarge or reduce the windows as "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Glavno okno v &kooka; sestavljeno iz treh okvirjev. Na vrhu si oglejte "
"plošči z ikonami in menijem. Z miško po potrebi povečajte ali pomanjšajte "
"okna."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The navigation window consists of three tabs, which allow you to switch "
"between the <guilabel>Scan</guilabel>, <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> and the "
"integrated file browser called the <guilabel>Gallery</guilabel>. The working "
"folder is displayed in the upper part of the window along with the folder "
"where the scan will be saved."
msgstr ""
"Navigacijsko okno je sestavljeno iz treh zavihkov, ki vam omogočajo "
"preklapljanje med <guilabel>Skeniranjem</guilabel>, <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> "
"in integriranim brskalnikom datotek, imenovanim <guilabel>Galerija</"
"guilabel>. Delovna mapa je prikazana v zgornjem delu okna skupaj z mapo, v "
"katero bo shranjen pregled."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make your scanner-dependent settings, which are dependent on the scanner you "
"have connected, in the lower left window. Usually, these are settings for "
"resolution, brightness and contrast, scanning mode (&eg;, color, gray, or "
"binary), and for gamma values."
msgstr ""
"V spodnjem levem oknu nastavite nastavitve, ki so odvisne od optičnega "
"bralnika, ki ste ga povezali. Običajno so to nastavitve za ločljivost, "
"svetlost in kontrast, način skeniranja (&eg; barvno, sivo ali binarno) in "
"vrednosti gama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure your settings here first. Afterwards, initiate the preview scan "
"with <guimenuitem>Preview</guimenuitem>. The scan result will then appear in "
"the right pane."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj najprej konfigurirajte svoje nastavitve. Nato zaženite pregled "
"predogleda s <guimenuitem>Predogled</guimenuitem>. Rezultat skeniranja se bo "
"nato prikazal v desnem podoknu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the area to scan in the preview image itself with the mouse to define "
"the final dimensions."
msgstr ""
"Z miško izberite območje za skeniranje v sami predogledni sliki, da določite "
"končne dimenzije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After this is done, click <guimenu>Scan</guimenu> to scan the selection made "
"in the preview. After scanning, you will be asked in which format to save "
"the image whether to make this your standard format (without being prompted "
"to confirm your selection in the future)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je to opravljeno, kliknite <guimenu>Skeniraj</guimenu>, da skenirate "
"izbor v predogledu. Po optičnem branju boste pozvani, v katerem formatu "
"želite shraniti sliko, ali naj bo to vaš standardni format (ne da bi morali "
"v prihodnje potrditi svojo izbiro)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you checked that you do not want to be asked about the save format, the "
"memory assistant will no longer appear. To change the format some time in "
"the future, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Configure Kooka...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Image Saving</"
"guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Always use the Save Assistant</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Če ste označili, da ne želite biti vprašani o formatu shranjevanja, pomočnik "
"za pomnilnik ne bo več prikazan. Če želite spremeniti obliko čez nekaj časa, "
"izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj Kooka ...</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Shranjevanje "
"slike</guimenuitem> <guimenuitem>Vedno uporabi pomočnika shranjevanja</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "The large window shows how the image appears after a final scan."
msgstr "Veliko okno prikazuje, kako je slika videti po končnem skeniranju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference and Configuration"
msgstr "Referenca in konfiguracija ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kooka; Menubar"
msgstr "&kooka; Menijska vrstica"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Folder...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova mapa...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new folder to hold your images in the <guilabel>Kooka Gallery</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite novo mapo za shranjevanje svojih slik v <guilabel>Galeriji Kooka</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save Image</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>S</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shrani sliko</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Save the image selected underneath the <guilabel>Kooka Gallery</guilabel> to "
"a different folder on your disk."
msgstr ""
"Shranite izbrano sliko pod <guilabel>Galerija Kooka</guilabel> v drugo mapo "
"na disku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "See the <link linkend=\"save\"> Save</link> section for details."
msgstr "Za podrobnosti glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"save\"> Shrani</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keysym>Del</keysym></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete Folder</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;<keysym>Del</keysym></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbriši mapo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete the folder selected underneath the <guilabel>Kooka Gallery</guilabel>."
msgstr "Izbrišite izbrano mapo pod <guilabel>Galerija Kooka</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Image From Selection</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova slika iz izbora</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the scanned image includes more than you want to appear in the final "
"image, use this tool to crop your image by marking your selection in the "
"larger image display to the right then selecting this tool. The image is "
"cropped according to your selection. You may already be familiar with this "
"function from &kolourpaint; crop tool."
msgstr ""
"Če optično prebrana slika vključuje več, kot želite videti na končni sliki, "
"s tem orodjem obrežite sliko tako, da označite svojo izbiro na zaslonu večje "
"slike na desni in nato izberete to orodje. Slika je obrezana glede na vaš "
"izbor. Morda že poznate to funkcijo iz &kolourpaint; orodje za obrezovanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Unload Image</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Odloži sliko</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remove the image displayed in the Image Viewer."
msgstr "Odstrani sliko, prikazano v pregledovalniku slik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prints the displayed image."
msgstr "Natisne prikazano sliko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &kooka;."
msgstr "Zapri &kooka;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Scan Menu"
msgstr "Meni skeniranja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Scan</guimenu> <guimenuitem>OCR Image...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Skeniraj</guimenu> <guimenuitem>OCR sliko...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start the optical character recognition (<acronym>OCR</acronym>) of the "
"whole image using the recognition system defined on the <guilabel>OCR</"
"guilabel> page in the settings dialog. This starts the character recognition "
"for the preview image."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite optično prepoznavanje znakov (<acronym>OCR</acronym>) celotne slike "
"z uporabo sistema za prepoznavanje, definiranega na strani <guilabel>OCR</"
"guilabel> v pogovornem oknu z nastavitvami. S tem se začne prepoznavanje "
"znakov za predogled slike."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Scan</guimenu> <guimenuitem>OCR Selection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Skeniraj</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izbira OCR...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A window will reappear for the character recognition. Here, however, the "
"character recognition is only for the area highlighted in the final scan."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno se bo pojavilo okno za prepoznavanje znakov. Tu pa je prepoznavanje "
"znakov samo za območje, ki je označeno v končnem skeniranju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Image Menu"
msgstr "Meni za slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The actions in this menu are also available in the context menu of the "
"preview window."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja v tem meniju so na voljo tudi v kontekstnem meniju okna za predogled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Scale to Width</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi na širino</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This proportionally scales the image in the large canvas to the width of the "
"display."
msgstr "To sorazmerno poveča sliko na velikem platnu glede na širino zaslona."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Scale to Height</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>H</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilagodi na višino</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:344
#, no-c-format
msgid "Proportionately scales the image to the height of the display."
msgstr "Sorazmerno poveča sliko glede na višino zaslona."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Original Size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvirna velikost</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Restores the original scan size by reducing or enlarging the image in the "
"display."
msgstr ""
"Obnovi izvirno velikost skeniranja tako, da zmanjša ali poveča sliko na "
"zaslonu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are additional methods of scaling an image: <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click the image display. Redefine the three named options and "
"set the enlargement itself. This can also be done in the <guilabel>Preview</"
"guilabel> window."
msgstr ""
"Obstajajo dodatni načini za spreminjanje velikosti slike: <mousebutton>z "
"desnim gumbom</mousebutton> kliknite prikaz slike. Ponovno določite tri "
"imenovane možnosti in nastavite samo povečavo. To lahko storite tudi v oknu "
"<guilabel>Predogled</guilabel>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:373
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mirror Vertically</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zrcaljenje navpično</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flip image vertically."
msgstr "Obrnite sliko navpično."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mirror Horizontally</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>M</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zrcaljenje vodoravno</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid "Flip image horizontally."
msgstr "Obrnite sliko vodoravno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>7</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rotate Counter-Clockwise</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>7</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zavrti v nasprotni smeri "
"urinega kazalca</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the image ninety degrees counterclockwise."
msgstr "Zavrti sliko za devetdeset stopinj v nasprotni smeri urinega kazalca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rotate Clockwise</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>9</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zavrti v smeri urinega "
"kazalca</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotate the image ninety degrees clockwise."
msgstr "Zavrti sliko za devetdeset stopinj v smeri urinega kazalca."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Image</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Rotate image 180 degrees</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>8</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Slika</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zavrti sliko za 180 stopinj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotates image 180 degrees."
msgstr "Zavrti sliko za 180 stopinj."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings Menu"
msgstr "Meni z nastavitvami"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menus described in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html"
"\">Menu</ulink> chapter of the &kde; Fundamentals documentation &kooka; has "
"these application specific menu entries:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg običajnega &kde; Menija <guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> in "
"<guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> sta opisana v poglavju <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html\">Meni</ulink> v &kde; Dokumentacija o osnovah "
"&kooka; ima te menijske vnose za posamezne aplikacije:"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:452
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select Scan Device...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberite napravo za skeniranje..."
"</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have several scanners use this action to select a scanner and use a "
"certain device always at startup."
msgstr ""
"Če imate več optičnih bralnikov, s tem dejanjem izberite optični bralnik in "
"ob zagonu vedno uporabite določeno napravo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add Scan Device...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj napravo za skeniranje...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:470
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a device which is not automatically detected at startup of &kooka;."
msgstr "Dodajte napravo, ki ni samodejno zaznana ob zagonu &kooka;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring Kooka"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje Kooke"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Splošno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the button in this section to reenable all messages and questions hidden "
"by using <guibutton>Don't ask me again</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Z gumbom v tem razdelku znova omogočite vsa sporočila in vprašanja, skrita z "
"<guibutton>Ne sprašuj me več</guibutton>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup"
msgstr "Začetek dela"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may want to uncheck <guilabel>Show the scanner selection dialog </"
"guilabel>, if you have only one scanner. If you have only one computer you "
"may also want to uncheck <guilabel>Query network for available scanners</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Morda boste želeli počistiti polje <guilabel>Prikaži pogovorno okno za "
"izbiro skenerja </guilabel>, če imate samo en skener. Če imate samo en "
"računalnik, boste morda želeli tudi počistiti polje <guilabel>Poizvedi "
"omrežje za razpoložljive optične bralnike</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "Image Saving"
msgstr "Shranjevanje slike"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Always use the Save Assistant</guilabel> <guilabel>Ask for "
"filename when saving</guilabel> <guilabel>Before the scan starts</"
"guilabel> / <guilabel>After the scan is finished</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Vedno uporabljaj pomočnika za shranjevanje</guilabel> "
"<guilabel>Pri shranjevanju vprašaj za ime datoteke</guilabel> <guilabel>Pred "
"začetkom skeniranja</guilabel> / <guilabel>Ko je skeniranje končano</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Gallery &amp; Thumbnails"
msgstr "Galerija &amp; Sličice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here the size of the thumbnails can be adjusted; as well as the background. "
"For example, you might want to reduce the size of the thumbnails if you are "
"scanning many pages from a book."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je mogoče prilagoditi velikost sličic; kot tudi ozadje. Na primer, "
"morda boste želeli zmanjšati velikost sličic, če skenirate veliko strani iz "
"knjige."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the section <guilabel>Image Gallery</guilabel> select how and where to "
"show the recent folders."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <guilabel>Galerija slik</guilabel> izberite, kako in kje "
"prikazati nedavne mape."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>OCR</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>OCR</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the OCR engine and the path to the executable."
msgstr "Izberite mehanizem OCR in pot do izvedljive datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid "Save"
msgstr "Shrani"

#. Tag: subtitle
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "More on Saving Images"
msgstr "Več o shranjevanju slik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:563
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The method for saving an image is somewhat different in &kooka; than in many "
"other applications. Click the <guilabel>Gallery</guilabel> tab to open a "
"small file browser. This is the folder <filename class=\"directory\">~/"
"Documents/KookaGallery</filename>. In the window, your current subfolder in "
"the gallery is shown. This is where all scanned images are first saved as "
"files. When starting &kooka; for the first time, you will only see the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">KookaGallery</filename>. Create subfolders by "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking this folder. The selected folder, "
"highlighted in blue, is the first save location of the scanned images. The "
"scans are labeled in ascending numerical order as in <filename>kscan_0001</"
"filename> and <filename>kscan_0002</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Metoda za shranjevanje slike je v &kooka; kot v mnogih drugih aplikacijah. "
"Kliknite zavihek <guilabel>Galerija</guilabel>, da odprete brskalnik majhnih "
"datotek. To je mapa <filename class=\"directory\">~/Documents/KookaGallery</"
"filename>. V oknu je prikazana vaša trenutna podmapa v galeriji. Tukaj se "
"vse optično prebrane slike najprej shranijo kot datoteke. Ko zaženete "
"&kooka; prvič boste videli samo <filename class=\"directory\">KookaGallery</"
"filename>. Ustvarite podmape tako, da <mousebutton>desno</mousebutton> "
"kliknete to mapo. Izbrana mapa, označena z modro, je prvo mesto shranjevanja "
"skeniranih slik. Skeniranja so označena v naraščajočem številčnem vrstnem "
"redu kot v <filename>kscan_0001</filename> in <filename>kscan_0002</"
"filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To save an image permanently, use <guimenuitem>Rename Image</guimenuitem> "
"and give a new name and the appropriate ending for the image format chosen "
"when scanning. If you enter a different extension, you will get a message "
"that it does not correspond to the scanned format. Although you can still "
"save the image under this name, it will retain its original format. At "
"present, <quote>On-the-fly</quote> conversion is not offered."
msgstr ""
"Če želite trajno shraniti sliko, uporabite <guimenuitem>Preimenuj sliko</"
"guimenuitem> in podajte novo ime in ustrezno končnico za format slike, "
"izbran pri skeniranju. Če vnesete drugo končnico, boste prejeli sporočilo, "
"da ne ustreza skenirani obliki. Čeprav lahko še vedno shranite sliko pod tem "
"imenom, bo ohranila prvotno obliko. Trenutno pretvorba <quote>Sproti</quote> "
"ni na voljo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not want to use this method of managing your images in <filename "
"class=\"directory\">~/Documents/KookaGallery/</filename>, you can, of "
"course, save them to another location. To do this, <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> click the image name and select <guilabel>Save Image</"
"guilabel>. Choose any path here. In addition, close or permanently delete "
"images here."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite uporabljati tega načina upravljanja svojih slik v <filename "
"class=\"directory\">~/Documents/KookaGallery/</filename>, jih seveda lahko "
"shranite na drugo mesto. Če želite to narediti, <mousebutton>desno</"
"mousebutton> kliknite ime slike in izberite <guilabel>Shrani sliko</"
"guilabel>. Tukaj izberite katero koli pot. Poleg tega tukaj zaprite ali "
"trajno izbrišite slike."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To incorporate other images in the gallery, use <menuchoice> <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Import Image</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> or add them by "
"dragging and dropping. Open the filemanager to the folder containing the "
"desired images. Then add them to the &kooka; gallery by dragging them and "
"dropping them into the gallery."
msgstr ""
"Če želite v galerijo vključiti druge slike, uporabite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi sliko</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> ali jih dodajte tako, da povlečete in spustite. Odprite "
"upravitelja datotek do mape, ki vsebuje želene slike. Nato jih dodajte v "
"&kooka; galeriji, tako da jih povlečete in spustite v galerijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Character Recognition"
msgstr "Prepoznavanje znakov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:603
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As already mentioned, the <application>gocr</application> must be installed. "
"Scan a preview of your document in grayscale or color. You can only scan in "
"binary mode if you have a pure white sheet of paper with black print. Next, "
"highlight the text to be recognized in the preview window. Then, do your "
"final scan in binary mode with <guibutton>Scan</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Kot že omenjeno, mora biti nameščen <application>gocr</application>. "
"Skenirajte predogled dokumenta v sivinah ali barvah. V binarnem načinu lahko "
"skenirate le, če imate čisto bel list papirja s črnim tiskom. Nato v oknu za "
"predogled označite besedilo, ki ga želite prepoznati. Nato izvedite končno "
"skeniranje v binarnem načinu z <guibutton>Skeniraj</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now click the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"ocr-"
"select.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon in the "
"toolbar, <guilabel>OCR Selection</guilabel>, or select this item in the "
"<guilabel>Scan</guilabel> menu. For your first try, do not change the "
"default settings shown in the emerging <acronym>OCR</acronym> window. These "
"are usually appropriate and meet most needs. Now click <guimenuitem>Start "
"OCR</guimenuitem>. You will now see a window containing the <acronym>OCR</"
"acronym> results. The quality depends heavily on that of the document itself."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj kliknite ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"ocr-"
"select.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> v orodni "
"vrstici, <guilabel>Izbira OCR</guilabel>, ali izberite ta element v meniju "
"<guilabel>Skeniraj</guilabel>. Pri prvem poskusu ne spreminjajte privzetih "
"nastavitev, prikazanih v pojavnem oknu <acronym>OCR</acronym>. Ti so "
"običajno primerni in ustrezajo večini potreb. Zdaj kliknite "
"<guimenuitem>Začni OCR</guimenuitem>. Zdaj boste videli okno z rezultati "
"<acronym>OCR</acronym>. Kakovost je v veliki meri odvisna od samega "
"dokumenta."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:622
#, no-c-format
msgid "The gocr Window"
msgstr "Okno gocr"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:625
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After character recognition is complete, start a spellcheck for the "
"recognized material. You can edit the content in the <guilabel>OCR</"
"guilabel> window and export it as plain text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je prepoznavanje znakov končano, zaženite preverjanje črkovanja za "
"prepoznano gradivo. Vsebino lahko urejate v oknu <guilabel>OCR</guilabel> in "
"jo izvozite kot navadno besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After the final scan, mark a selection in the image display to the right to "
"load just a part of the text or image to the <acronym>OCR</acronym>. Next, "
"in the toolbar, click the <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"ocr-select.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icon "
"or click in the menu on <guimenuitem>OCR Selection</guimenuitem>. Now "
"proceed as described in the previous section."
msgstr ""
"Po končnem skeniranju označite izbor na slikovnem prikazu na desni, da "
"naložite le del besedila ali slike v <acronym>OCR</acronym>. Nato v orodni "
"vrstici kliknite ikono <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"ocr-select.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> ali v "
"meniju kliknite <guimenuitem> Izbira OCR</guimenuitem>. Zdaj nadaljujte, kot "
"je opisano v prejšnjem razdelku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:638
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Results of the <acronym>OCR</acronym>"
msgstr "Rezultati <acronym>OCR</acronym>"

